resources.string: First you need to beat my robot in Tic Tac Toe. A botton will pop up when you beat it for you to continue. Feel free to relax for as long as you want. Remember resting is important.
Take a little rest and look at some foxes with some random non-important but interesting facts to take your mind off of the stress!
Stay for as long as you want. Click on the fact to change the picture of the fox and the fact itself!
P.S. Remember nothing saves feel free to talk about everything you want!
Don\'t forget to take a break.\nReflection is the beginning of improvement.
